      • convertRouteLevel1ToLevel2

        public static java.util.Optional<IsisRoute> convertRouteLevel1ToLevel2(IsisRoute route,
                                                                       int l2Admin)
        Convert a level-1 IS-IS route to a level-2 IS-IS route. All route attributes except level/protocol and the admin distance remain unchanged.
        Parameters:
        route - the route to convert
        l2Admin - the new L2 admin distance to use.
        Returns:
        an optional of IsisRoute. It will be empty if the route given is not level 1 or has its down bit set.
